    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 across the full CPB operating envelope with GCI < 5%. The credibility assessment team accepted the simulation team's determination that the rc2 validation build is functionally equivalent to the released ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7 solver based on the configuration management change-log review, and no re-execution of the validation matrix was deemed necessary prior to submission.",
